name: Self-Actualization
description: Surrealistrasyon/Şerif Gümüşbaş/Digital art/1800x2700/We take refuge in creativity in every step taken from the usual to uncertainty to realize itself./I have been drawing for years as a result of my interest in drawing since my childhood. And I am 32 years old. In this period of time, the automatism method I discovered over time has been the best tool for describing myself and the world I experience. I love to often think, write and exchange ideas on these pictures that I convey my unconscious
